 11 | ## Endpoints
 12 | 
 13 | - `GET /api/users` — List all users
 14 | - `POST /api/users` — Create a new user
 15 | - `GET /api/health` — Health check
 16 | 
 17 | ## Running
 18 | 
 19 | ```bash
 20 | sbt run
 21 | ```
 22 | 
 23 | ## Architecture
 24 | 
 25 | The app uses a simple controller pattern. Each route maps to a handler function
 26 | that takes a `Request` and returns a `Response`.
 27 | 
